lead_paragraph: Big guns Bradley Wiggins and Mark Cavendish will bolster the British team for next month's Olympic track cycling program but the powerhouse nation will have its work cut out repeating the supremacy of four years ago in London.

headline.print_headline: Wiggo, Cav Back but British Supremacy Faces Test
